short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A secure file management system for Gmail

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Immunefiles is a cutting-edge, secure file-sharing platform now available as a Gmail extension. Designed to enhance both the security and efficiency of file sharing within your organization, Immunefiles integrates advanced security features with user-friendly functionality. This platform aims to protect sensitive information, streamline collaboration, and ensure that your data remains secure during all stages of sharing and access. Immunefiles extension offers Proctored Sharing, Password-Protected Link, Access Limit,  Screenshot Prevention, Scheduled Link Expiration, Real-Time Log Generation and more!
